=\"_blank\">https://event.881903.com/hktbaudioplayer/player_token.php?ch=hd881</a><br />\n<br />\n商業電台903商業二台直播網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://event.881903.com/hktbaudioplayer/player_token.php?ch=hd903\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevent.881903.com%2Fhktbaudioplayer%2Fplayer_token.php%3Fch%3Dhd903&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2Bgy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=19aacab9\" target=\"_blank\">https://event.881903.com/hktbaudioplayer/player_token.php?ch=hd903</a><br />\n<br />\nNow新聞332台直播網頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flive&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2Bgy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=357a1981\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flive&h=73f2783e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/live</a><br />\n<br />\nNow新聞時事全方位網頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/feature/detail?catCode=124&amp;topicId=566\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffeature%2Fdetail%3FcatCode%3D124%26topicId%3D566&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2Bgy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=41832d5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffeature%2Fdetail%3FcatCode%3D124%26topicId%3D566&h=0f43012e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/feature/detail?catCode=124&amp;topicId=566</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有關打電話Phone-In既要點<br />\n<br />\n1)　姓氏係可以化名！超重要！佢唔會查你身份證，姓氏係可以作！<br />\n2)　要注意係電台電視台會篩人，所以內容要夠爆<br />\n3)　內容係公開，所以唔好自爆！唔好講太多個人特徵同個人資料！<br />\n4)　主持為左個節目keep住有觀眾講野，所以內容一定要精而簡！講野最緊要唔好有停頓。一停佢就cut你線。要準備好比人cut線既心理準備<br />\n5)　打上去鳩講係 ok的。重點係佔據大氣電波，因為好多要警察開實彈既人會打去！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我暫時自己只係嘗試過打Now時事全方位<br />\n要返工 次次都要消失個幾鐘mon住個電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBetween<br />\n打上去<br />\n留底你既姓(可以化名)<br />\n再加少少意見<br />\n然後等Call back<br />\n<br />\n要注意！<br />\n第一！1833298未必一定通<br />\n我試過1次通，亦有3次通，更加有103次通<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二！1833298通左未必有Call back<br />\n我3次成功，只有一次Call back<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係！<br />\n大家唔好放棄！繼續一齊8點起mon住個商台再mon住個now；或者淨係mon住港台或者Now；放工再一齊mon住港台！<br />\n我自己係每日返工都必定由8點聽881到10點再轉去Now聽時事全方位<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">I am watching you.</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一齊打上去佔據大氣電波啊！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b984b4c58b524b1bfc3b015f823b9de47fb5ee","tid":1463680,"uid":296712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:33:59.000Z","msg":"打到一個字都無淨啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e69ca82abd321ec733751205394e628eca232d","tid":1463680,"uid":296712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:35:48.000Z","msg":"應該要等到聽朝先會有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9fb058b9ff83950bf018e6a0e7ed44235ed1008","tid":1463680,"uid":134508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:02:42.000Z","msg":"又幫你推"},{"pid":"5b7f6b6e1046b598ab85df79ebd5ae050ce6a54d","tid":1463680,"uid":184279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:44:09.000Z","msg":"千禧8-10"},{"pid":"4968353460e41e78b8663561b612ca82100d255a","tid":1463680,"uid":184279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:45:55.000Z","msg":"時事全方位星期二轉咗肥仔聰"},{"pid":"65bcb4adfc0607bdf22f04c4ba6d7702d72b640c","tid":1463680,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"