br />\n因為星期日既事件令示威者變成驚弓之鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n90後攬炒巴黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cdbd7b1d5578b1adc42055015abb52f5425976d","tid":1463680,"uid":296712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:48:20.000Z","msg":"李小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講和理非既重要性<br />\n但係佢熱淨企道德高地<br />\n要沉著氣贏和理非既掌手<br />\n例如諗下點避開啲鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3X歲和理非面具 真勇武心<br />\n好多朋友 和理面 勇武心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d2fb483db60a089a5961a1f3d5d366418f2cb4","tid":1463680,"uid":296712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:50:39.000Z","msg":"黃生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n口罩令示威者變激進<br />\n委任證令警察變激進<br />\n網絡活動現實化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫傳媒叫所有人除低口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73891be2e4ab0248abf94a2c217929b92a46f0c2","tid":1463680,"uid":274774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:52:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e26cab0445db2699f933958d7b51d0b522fa2206","tid":1463680,"uid":296712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:55:56.000Z","msg":"楊生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港係一國既一部份<br />\n我地係中國人<br />\n對外國既教育太少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3983095bd3c4e87576e1d90ca9805095f48169","tid":1463680,"uid":296712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:59:33.000Z","msg":"盧太<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第一次打黎<br />\n<br />\n68返港<br />\n69就無去<br />\n100萬人喎 點解會無回應<br />\n好冷漠啊<br />\n<br />\n無回應係失策<br />\n話612係暴動好傷心<br />\n<br />\n64係青年人<br />\n係香港見到64重現 好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期日有去機場<br />\n遊行全部有去架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期日好和平架<br />\n<br />\n警察記者會又火上加油<br />\n818一齊行出黎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實示威者好多人都好冷靜架<br />\n得兩三個係激動少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好驚嚇到啲人唔敢再去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e7669ba5c68452276428361728abfe8038d533","tid":1463680,"uid":296712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:00:45.000Z","msg":"0814<br />\n是日時事全方位結束<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}